question:
What kind of collection is this?

```sql
DECLARE
  TYPE t_names IS TABLE OF VARCHAR2(50) INDEX BY PLS_INTEGER;
  v_names t_names;
BEGIN
  v_names(1) := 'Ali';
  DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(v_names(1));
END;
```

What does this declare?

```sql
DECLARE
  TYPE t_emp IS RECORD (
    id   NUMBER,
    name VARCHAR2(50)
  );
  v_emp t_emp;
BEGIN
  v_emp.id := 1;
  v_emp.name := 'Ali';
END;
```
